import { Card, CardActionArea, CardContent, CardMedia, Paper, Typography } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'
import Carousel from 'react-material-ui-carousel'

const MainTopSection = () => {
  
  

  return (
    <>
    <Card sx={{ maxWidth: '300px' , maxHeight:'400px' , objectFit:'cover' }}>
      <CardActionArea>
        <CardMedia
          component="img"
          sx={{ width: '100%', height: '100%', objectFit: 'cover' }}
          image="/images/category/matrix.jpg"
          alt="matrix"
        />
        <CardContent>
          <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="div">
            매트릭스
          </Typography>
        </CardContent>
      </CardActionArea>
    </Card>

    </>
  )
}

export default MainTopSection
